      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0564P0-05403'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0564P0_19950607_GCR_189' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The noble Lord said: Three amendments run together, Amendments Nos. 120 to 122. I have had the opportunity
        <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_92gc' title='Col. 92GC &mdash; HL Deb 07 June 1995 vol 564 c92GC' name='column_92gc' href='#column_92gc' rel='bookmark'>92GC</a>
